Parking Lot requirements

1. Multiple floors
2. Multiple entry gates
3. entry ticket is generated
4. ticket contains- entry time,parking slot, vehicle type vehicle no
5. one floor can have multiple parking lots
6. different types of vehicle supported
7. Payment- Partial payment option
8. Different types of slot for different vehicles
9. special slot for special vehicles
10. Bill is calculated at exit gate
11. Payment to be done at exit gate
12 Multiple types of payments accepted

Clarify the requirements
1. Support multiple ways of slot allocation
2. Bill calculation -> duration of parking
                    -> Type of vehicle
3. Payment supported-> partial payments
                    -> multiple modes cash/online
4. separate pricing for electric cars

